The paper deals with the problem of gathering for mobile robots, which is a classic problem in robotics and falls under the category of robotics and control (cs.RO). The paper also involves the use of algorithms and computation to solve the problem, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also involves decision-making and optimization, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
